{"tid":1496334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"光復入境處","createTime":"2019-08-22T13:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T14:35:16.000Z","uid":227379,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a78e889bfecd646fa9d289028a4009005da207af","tid":1496334,"uid":227379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得入境處都一定要光復下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概想表達既就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，每日有150名大陸人入黎香港，呢個都係惡法係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但就好似無一啲實際大型行動去表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然都知道「反送中」運動都減少左好多既大陸人，但覺得都係唔夠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意思係其實政府用警隊都只係明刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但政府用入境處先係暗箭，市民而家都係掛住擋緊警隊明刀，但入境處日日批百五 不斷不斷射緊箭入黎 而大家冇理到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者唔夠針對性表達。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望黎緊之後既運動，會有一次有關入境處事務既運動。既然而家都開始少左大陸人黎香港，不如順水推舟，加強抵制大陸人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa25f9fec21a691d45728054049f10c058837bf2","tid":1496334,"uid":227379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4faaf8aacd8d55abaf33cde1ced82800d366e5fc","tid":1496334,"uid":227379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c5d917bbd201ee9d71775f4444659cf166d21a04","tid":1496334,"uid":227379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"aa059baf8435f7ce5858028052f854ccc2bed879","tid":1496334,"uid":227379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8ab4fd441aae7ab99edb41a4ce9fc6901a510a25","tid":1496334,"uid":91321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"入境好多手足<br />\n但更多藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822ab930bf7c934c6b1375648418ce31a9c07dd5","tid":1496334,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"邊間？<br />\nBtw總部係灣仔"},{"pid":"8bf9cb51bd2a270b27a923d41b82088a653813c9","tid":1496334,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab4fd441aae7ab99edb41a4ce9fc6901a510a25","tid":1496334,"uid":91321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:18:08.000Z","ms